data.description: Lowest priced and largest Penthouse in the building! 3 BR/2 BA corner-unit features a SW exposure, incredible views of the sunsets. This unit does not have a balcony, safe for pets and small children. Granite countertops, Italian cabinetry and stainless steel appliances; Double-basin stainless steel under-mounted sink; Designer floor tile; Bathrooms features: marble counter tops, Wall-to-wall vanity mirror, designer floor and wall tile, 42'' tubs in Master Bath, and designer fixtures. Track lighting in dining room. Impact-resistant windows and sliding doors. Community includes a 76 slip deep-water marina with convenient access to ocean and 22,000 sq. ft. of shops including waterfront restaurants. This is a perfect opportunity to experience resort-style living at a fraction of the cost!
